strings:
<voice_0x01001678><center>Our beautiful world and our future
<center>are now in your hands. keep your head up...

<voice_0x01001679><center>Dear family, we take care of you
<center>and say goodbye to the end of the kingdom...

<voice_0x0100167C><se_low><center>If you break my black armor, you will rot
<center>in hell! But first you must taste
<center>the true might of my flesh and blood!

<voice_0x0100167D><se_low><center>until death consoles you,
<center>you will be afraid forever
